      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "优胜劣汰，适者生存，这背后其实是一种强大的搜索算法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "如果让计算机也来模拟进化，它能替我们找到问题的最优解吗？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "这就是遗传算法，一种向生命学来的优化方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "fitness",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "fitness-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/fitness-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "我们要在一条起伏的地形上，找到最高的那座山峰。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "fitness",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "fitness-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/fitness-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "每个候选解就是一个个体，它所在的高度就是它的适应度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "fitness",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "fitness-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/fitness-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "适应度越高，代表这个解越好，越值得被保留。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "operators",
      "line_id": "op-1",
      "filename": "operators-op-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/operators-op-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "选择：适应度高的个体，更有机会成为下一代的父母。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "operators",
      "line_id": "op-2",
      "filename": "operators-op-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/operators-op-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "交叉：两个父母的解相互组合，孕育出新的后代。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "operators",
      "line_id": "op-3",
      "filename": "operators-op-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/operators-op-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "变异：以小概率随机扰动，让种群不至于陷入局部山头。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "converge-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/converge-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "一代又一代，散落各处的个体渐渐聚拢到最高的山峰。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "genetic-algorithm",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "converge-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/genetic-algorithm/xiaoxiao/converge-con-2.mp3",
